metadata.name: Minimal Universe - self
metadata.description:
Nothing but everything. Self is like that which is sometimes seems nothing but when time comes you will see the complexity and the wholeness in connections even in a single creature. The beginning of the scene was merely nothing out of the boring sunshine but now it has been on its life so far for over 10 years. Who knows it would live forever in the connected relationship bewteen physical and emotional status. Feel the whole thing, focus on the line, sound and yourself. 

1920x1080, 45sec, mp4, 2022
